					<p style="color: var(--text-inverse); font-size: 0.65rem; opacity: 0.6; margin: 0;">
						Open source under <a href="/LICENSE" style="color: var(--teal-crystal); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.3s ease;" onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--amber-glow)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--teal-crystal)'" title="View full license terms">MIT License</a>
